Definition: a Japanese shrub that resembles members of the genus Spiraea
Example: widely cultivated in many varieties for its dense panicles of flowers in many colors; often forced by florists for Easter blooming
Synonyms: spiraea, Astilbe_japonica, astilbe, a, Japanese, shrub, that, resembles, members, of, the, genus, Spiraea, widely, cultivated, in, many, varieties, for, its, dense, panicles, flowers, colors, often, forced, by, florists, Easter, blooming
Category: noun.plant
